# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians6.rpy:16
translate chinese adrians6_b9aed4a7:

    # gg "No, not at the moment."
    gg "不，目前没有。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians6.rpy:18
translate chinese adrians6_f3b60fea:

    # gg "I have my driver's license and I drive my mom's car sometimes, but I haven't been able to afford a car of my own yet."
    gg "我有驾照，有时会开我妈的车，但我还没买得起自己的车。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians6.rpy:20
translate chinese adrians6_bb61b60f:

    # gg "What I'd really like is a motorcycle."
    gg "我真正想要的是摩托车。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians6.rpy:21
translate chinese adrians6_4d4cf96f:

    # pc "Oh, really?"
    pc "哦，真的吗？"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians6.rpy:22
translate chinese adrians6_533a6b28:

    # gg "Yeah!"
    gg "是的！"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians6.rpy:23
translate chinese adrians6_cf41a7d1:

    # gg "My cousin Athena rides one and she taught me how one time when I visited her."
    gg "我表妹雅典娜骑摩托车，有次我去她那儿玩，她教过我一次。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians6.rpy:24
translate chinese adrians6_dc53d16e:

    # gg "It was so much fun. And motorcycles are just fucking cool, right?"
    gg "那感觉太棒了。而且摩托车简直酷毙了，对吧？"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians6.rpy:25
translate chinese adrians6_cded8a02:

    # pc "They are cool. Dangerous though."
    pc "确实很酷。不过挺危险的。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians6.rpy:26
translate chinese adrians6_a10a7ac0:

    # gg "Yeah, but that's part of what makes them cool!"
    gg "是啊，但这正是它酷的地方！"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians6.rpy:28
translate chinese adrians6_b4234ad6:

    # gg "Besides, the speed limit on every street in Skyhill is like 30 miles per hour."
    gg "再说，斯凯希尔每条街的限速也就30英里一小时。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians6.rpy:29
translate chinese adrians6_da1f8c49:

    # gg "I'm not gonna be riding it on {i}der Autobahn{/i} or anything."
    gg "我又不是要在{i}德国高速公路{/i}上骑。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians6.rpy:30
translate chinese adrians6_d0c89101:

    # pc "I guess that's true."
    pc "这话倒也是。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians6.rpy:32
translate chinese adrians6_ae1f8952:

    # gg "Anyway, need money first, but I'd like to get one some day."
    gg "总之，得先攒够钱，但我真想哪天能拥有一辆。"

